Isolation forest is clustering method, so it could be replaced by kmeans (another clustering method) to finish the task in assignment 2

Isolation forest returns the value and the higher value means higher chance of being anomaly

Isolation forest could work with parameter searching method to find out the best model with the object function on error metrics such as accuracy.

Isolation forest would still work if your time series data is not stationary
